\c 11
\s Pauro unozvidavirira pamabasa ake
\p
\v 1 Dai muchindiitira moyo murefu zvishoma paupenzi \add hwangu\add*; asi nemwi munondiitira moyo murefu.
\v 2 Nekuti ndine godo nemwi negodo reuMwari; nekuti ndakakuwanisai kumurume umwe, kuti ndiku\add ku\add*mikidze\add i\add* \add muri\add* mhandara yakachena kuna Mwari.
\v 3 Asi ndinotya kuti zvimwe nyoka sezvayakanyengera Eva nemano ayo, saizvozvo ndangariro dzenyu dzingatsauswa pakururama kuri muna Kristu.
\v 4 Nekuti kana unosvika achiparidza umwe Jesu watisina kuparidza, kana muchigamuchira umwe mweya wamusina kugamuchira, kana imwe evhangeri yamusina kugamuchira, zvakanaka mu\add mu\add*itire moyo murefu.
\v 5 Nekuti ndinoti handitairi nepaduku kuvaapositori vakurusa.
\v 6 Zvino kunyange ndisina kudzidza pashoko, asi kwete paruzivo; asi pachinhu chose takaratidzwa kwamuri muzvinhu zvose.
\v 7 Kana ndakaita chivi here pakuzvininipisa kuti imwi mukudzwe, nekuti ndakaparidza kwamuri evhangeri yaMwari pasina muripo?
\v 8 Ndakapamba dzimwe kereke, ndichitora muripo kuti ndikubatsirei.
\v 9 Uye pandakange ndiripo kwamuri ndichishaiwa handina kuremedza munhu; nekuti zvandaishaiwa, hama dzaibva Makedhonia dzakapa; uye pazvose ndakachenjera kuti ndirege kuva mutoro kwamuri, uye ndicha\add zvi\add*chengeta.
\v 10 \add Sezvo\add* chokwadi chaKristu chiri mandiri, kuti kuzvikudza uku hakungamiswi mandiri kumatunhu eAkaya.
\v 11 Nemhaka yei? Nekuti handikudiyi here? Mwari unoziva.
\v 12 Asi chandinoita, ndichaitawo, kuti ndigure mukana kune vanoshuva mukana; kuti pane zvavanozvikudza nazvo vawanikwe vakaita sesuwo.
\v 13 Nekuti vakadaro vaapositori venhema, vabati vanonyengera, vanozvishandura kuva vaapositori vaKristu.
\v 14 Hazvishamisiwo; nekuti Satani amene unozvishandura kuva mutumwa wechiedza.
\v 15 Naizvozvo ha\add chi\add*si chinhu chikuru kana nevashumiri vake vachizvishandura \add kuita\add* sevashumiri vekururama; kuguma kwawo kuchava semabasa avo.
\s Kutambudzika kwaPauro pamusoro peevhangeri
\p
\v 16 Ndinotizve: Ngakurege kuva nemunhu unofunga kuti ndiri benzi; asi kana zvisaka\add daro\add*, sebenzi ndigamuchirei, kuti neni ndizvikudze zvishoma.
\v 17 Izvo zvandinotaura, handitauri muna Ishe, asi sepaupenzi, pachivimbo ichi chekuzvikudza.
\v 18 Sezvo vazhinji vachizvikudza panyama, iniwo ndichazvikudza.
\v 19 Nekuti munoitira mapenzi moyo murefu nemufaro, imwi muri vakachenjera.
\v 20 Nekuti munoita moyo murefu, kana munhu achikuisai muuranda, kana munhu achi\add ku\add*dyai kupedza, kana munhu achi\add ku\add*tapa\add i\add*, kana munhu achizvikudza, kana munhu achikurovai kumeso.
\v 21 Ndinoreva sechinyadzo, kusvika senge isu takange tine utera. Zvino kana kune munhu une ushingi (ndinotaura paupenzi), ini ndine ushingiwo.
\v 22 VaHebheru here? Neni\add wo\add*. VaIsraeri here? Neni\add wo\add*. Imbeu yaAbhurahamu here? Neni\add wo\add*.
\v 23 Vashumiri vaKristu here? (Ndinotaura \add se\add*mupengo), ndino\add va\add*pfuura, zvikuru pamabasa anorema zvakapamhidzirwa kwazvo, pamavanga kupfuura chipimo, mumajere kakadzokororwa kwazvo, pandufu kazhinji.
\v 24 KuvaJudha ndakagamuchira kashanu, \add shamhu\add* dzine makumi mana kusiya imwe.
\v 25 Katatu ndakarohwa netsvimbo, kamwe ndakatakwa nemabwe, katatu ndakaputsikirwa nechikepe usiku hwumwe nemasikati ndakange ndiri muudziku \add hwegungwa\add*;
\v 26 \add pa\add*nzendo kazhinji, \add pa\add*njodzi dzenzizi, \add pa\add*njodzi dzemakororo, \add pa\add*njodzi nevekwangu, \add pa\add*njodzi nevahedheni, \add pa\add*njodzi muguta, \add pa\add*njodzi murenje, \add pa\add*njodzi mugungwa, \add pa\add*njodzi pakati pehama dzenhema;
\v 27 pakutambudzika nepakuremerwa, pakusavata kazhinji, panzara nenyota, pakutsanya kazhinji, pachando nepakushama.
\v 28 kunze kwezvinhu izvi zviri panze, zvinondimanikidza zuva rimwe nerimwe, kurangarira kereke dzose.
\v 29 Ndiani unoshaiwa simba, neni ndikasashaiwa simba? Ndiani unogumburwa, neni ndikasatsva?
\v 30 Kana zvakafanira kuzvikudza, ndichazvikudza nezvinhu zveutera hwangu.
\v 31 Mwari naBaba vaIshe wedu Jesu Kristu, unorumbidzwa kusvikira rinhi narinhi, unoziva kuti handirevi nhema.
\v 32 PaDhamasiko mutungamiriri waishe Areta wakarinda guta reveDhamasiko achitsvaka kundibata;
\v 33 uye ndakaburuswa nepawindo \add ndiri\add* mudengu nepamudhuri, ndikapukunyuka pamaoko ake.
